<template><div><h1 id="for-in-语句" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#for-in-语句"><span>for-in 语句</span></a></h1>
<p><code v-pre>for-in</code> 语句用于遍历数组或者对象的属性（对数组或者对象的属性进行循环操作）。</p>
<h2 id="语法" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#语法"><span>语法</span></a></h2>
